#TitanFamilyFeature: Let's play ball! ⚾️

🔸Jason Dietrich, @csufalumni '99, was introduced as the new head @fullertonbsb coach at a press conference on Goodwin Field yesterday. 

🔹“I’m so very honored and humbled to get this great opportunity to be the leader of Cal State Fullerton,” Dietrich said. 

🔸Dietrich, the sixth head coach in the program’s Division I history, comes to #CSUF after spending the last two seasons as the pitching coach at East Carolina where he helped lead the team to the @ncaa Super Regionals this year.
